               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1828" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1828" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1828" type="surname" value="LANEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1828" type="given" value="DAVID DE"></interp>DAVID DE LANEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a cheesemonger. The prisoner came to my shop on the 12th of August for a quarter of a pound of cheese—he gave me a shilling—I found it was bad—I asked him where he got it—he said he was not aware it was bad—I gave him and the shilling to the officer.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1829" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1829" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1829" type="surname" value="CONSTABLE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1829" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN CONSTABLE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable M</hi> 43.) I took the prisoner—as I was taking him to the station, there is an open ditch near to the shop—he put his hand to his mouth, and threw a quantity of coin into the ditch—two shillings rested on the side of the ditch—I kept my eye on them till I saw them got by the street-keeper—these are them, and this is the one I got from Mr. De Laney.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1830" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1830" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1830" type="surname" value="FIELD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1830" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>MR. JOHN FIELD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am inspector of coin to the Mint. These shillings are all counterfeit, and cast in the same mould.</p>
